.TH graph_2_mat 1 "September 1995" "Scilab Group" "Scilab function"
.so man1/sci.an
.SH NAME
graph_2_mat - node-arc incidence matrix from graph
.SH CALLING SEQUENCE
.nf
[a] = graph_2_mat(g)
.fi
.SH PARAMETERS
.TP 2
g
: graph-list
.TP 2
a
: sparse node-arc incidence matrix
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fVgraph_2_mat\fR computes the node-arc incidence matrix corresponding
to the graph \fVg\fR.
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
g=load_graph(SCI+'/demos/metanet/colored');
a=graph_2_mat(g)
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
mat_2_graph
